(This homework introduces the Pintos intrusive linked-list implementation and) Tj T*
(uses it in a word-count program. It also introduces basic pthread programming:) Tj T*
(the pwords executable should spawn worker threads, process input files in) Tj T*
(parallel, and wait for all workers before printing the final result.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
