(- word_count_p.c: thread-aware word-count storage and synchronization.) Tj T*
(- pwords.c: create one thread per input file and join every spawned thread.) Tj T*
(- pthread.c: smaller pthread practice program.) Tj T*
(- gutenberg/: larger input files for comparison and stress testing.) Tj T*
